{{#extend "mail/layouts/main"}}
  {{#content "headerTitle"}}
      【FreshLinker】Congratulations! Your Company is approved.<br/>
      【FreshLinker】恭喜！我們已通過你添加公司申請.
  {{/content}}

  {{#content "content"}}
      <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">
          <tr>
              <td class="aligncenter content-block">
                  <h2 style="text-align: left;">Hi {{email}}:</h2>
              </td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
              <td>
                  <span style="margin: 0 20px 0 0px; display: inline-block;">
                 Congrats! Your newly added company【{{company.name}}】 Company is now approved, please simply click the below link to login to your account.
                      Get started by updating your company details, and we will provide you a recruitment experience unlike another.<br/>
                  恭喜你！我們審核並通過了你添加公司【{{company.name}}】公司的申請，請點擊下方按鈕登入你的帳戶，並完善公司資料，以享受我們為你提供的優質招聘服務。
                  </span>
              </td>
          </tr>
          <tr style="display:block; margin-top: 35px; margin-bottom: 35px;">
              <td>
                  <a href="{{sourceUrl}}/enterprise/login" class="btn-primary"
                     style="display: inline-block; padding: 0 30px; line-height: 1em;" target="_blank">
                      View Company (前往查看)
                  </a>
              </td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
              <td>
                  <span style="margin: 35px 20px 0 0px; display: inline-block;">
                  Need help along the way? Please feel free to contact us at +852 3547 2513 or email us at support@freshlinker.com.<br/>
                  如果你有任何問題，請立即致電+852 3547 2513或電郵至support@freshlinker.com聯絡我們。
                  </span>

              </td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
              <td>
                  <span style="margin: 35px 20px 0 0px; display: inline-block;">
                    Cheers,<br/>
                    FreshLinker
                  </span>
              </td>
          </tr>

          <tr>
              <td class="content-block" style="display: inline-block; margin-top: 40px;">
                  *This is an automatically generated email, please do not reply.<br/>
                  *此為系統自動發送的電郵，請勿直接回覆。
              </td>
          </tr>
      </table>
  {{/content}}
{{/extend}}
